trans-unit.source: The <see cref="N:System.Xml.Resolvers" /> namespace provides support for prepopulating the cache with DTDs or XML streams.
trans-unit.target: El espacio de nombres de <see cref="N:System.Xml.Resolvers" /> proporciona compatibilidad con el rellenado previo de DTD y secuencias XML en la memoria caché.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers> namespace defines the <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> and the <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlKnownDtds> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers> espacio de nombres define la <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> y <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlKnownDtds> enumeración.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> is used as a resolver when automatic calls to the network are not desired or are not possible.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> se utiliza como una resolución cuando no se desean o no son posibles llamadas automáticas a la red.

trans-unit.source: For example, this type can be used for loading cached external DTDs.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, este tipo puede usarse para cargar las DTD externas almacenado en caché.

trans-unit.source: Another scenario is loading XHTML and using <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> to preload well-known DTDs that are defined in XHTML 1.0.
trans-unit.target: Otro escenario es cargar XHTML y utilizar <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> para cargar previamente DTD conocidas que se definen en XHTML 1.0.

trans-unit.source: Preloading a well-known DTD does not invoke any network connections because these DTDs are already embedded in the System.Xml.Utils assembly.
trans-unit.target: Cargar previamente una DTD conocida no invoca las conexiones de red porque estas DTD ya están incrustadas en el ensamblado System.Xml.Utils.

trans-unit.source: Currently, <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> includes XHTML 1.0 and RSS 0.91 DTDs.
trans-unit.target: Actualmente, <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> incluye XHTML 1.0 y RSS 0.91 DTD.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlKnownDtds> enumeration defines which well-known DTDs the <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> recognizes.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlKnownDtds> enumeración define las DTD conocidas que el <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> reconoce.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlKnownDtds> enumeration contains the `Xhtml10`, `Rss091`, `All`, and `None` values.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlKnownDtds> enumeración contiene la `Xhtml10`, `Rss091`, `All`, y `None` valores.

trans-unit.source: `XmlKnownDtd.Xhtml10` specifies that the `T:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver` will recognize DTDs and entities that are defined in XHTML 1.0.
trans-unit.target: `XmlKnownDtd.Xhtml10` Especifica que el `T:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver` reconocerá las DTD y entidades que se definen en XHTML 1.0.

trans-unit.source: For more information about XHTML, see the [XHTML 1.0 specification](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=109812).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información sobre XHTML, consulte el [especificación XHTML 1.0](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=109812).

trans-unit.source: `XmlKnownDtd.Rss091` specifies that the `T:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver` will recognize DTDs and entities that are defined in RSS 0.91.
trans-unit.target: `XmlKnownDtd.Rss091` Especifica que el `T:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver` reconocerá las DTD y entidades definidas en RSS 0.91.

trans-unit.source: `XmlKnownDtd.All` specifies that the <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> will recognize all currently supported DTDs.
trans-unit.target: `XmlKnownDtd.All` Especifica que el <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> reconocerá todas las DTD compatibles actualmente.

trans-unit.source: `XmlKnownDtd.None` specifies that the <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> will not recognize any of the predefined DTDs.
trans-unit.target: `XmlKnownDtd.None` Especifica que el <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> no reconocerá ninguna de las DTD predefinidas.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> preloads a well-known DTD, it does not invoke network connections because the DTDs are already embedded in the System.Xml.Utils assembly.
trans-unit.target: Cuando el <xref:System.Xml.Resolvers.XmlPreloadedResolver> carga previamente una DTD conocida, no invoca las conexiones de red porque las DTD ya están incrustadas en el ensamblado System.Xml.Utils.
